reviews.review_text: 12-10-79 Audience version, somewhat muddied by hiss / background noise.  Too bad because it sounds like a good performance.  I'm off to look for other, clearer copies.  Peace.

BEST TRUCKIN' This is one of, if not THE best Truckin' ever!!  Great energy!!! 

This is one of the few sources in circulation...same as my old analog cassette that I wore out years ago.
